displayName: City of Martial Arts, Jinami. Collector Renta's House

parameters:
Collector Renta: Take a look at this collection! I've been
diligently collecting these since I was a child!
Clea: I came from the Adventurer's Guild in Ftera.

Collector Renta: Welcome! I'm glad you came! I'd like to
explain the details of the request!

Clea: I see... So all I have to do is participate in the
martial arts tournament and obtain the crown, right?

Collector Renta: The crown associated with the mighty king
Pizuma, who is renowned in the arena, is the object of
desire for collectors!

Collector Renta: I may not be of fighting age... and even if
I were younger, I wouldn't have the courage to participate.
Thief Nora: I-Is it really that difficult...?

Collector Renta: The mighty king Pizuma, renowned as the
king of defense, withstood the fierce attacks of the strong
warriors of Valt and emerged victorious.

Collector Renta: Based on that legend, the martial arts
tournament this time will have fierce beasts like the
warriors of Valt as opponents.
Collector Renta: I'm praying for your victory!

Collector Renta: I plan to adorn the crown in the best
place, praying for your victory!

Collector Renta: I was watching the battles in the arena! I
never expected General Atu to show up!
Clea: This will be the promised crown.

Collector Renta: Amazing... What beauty...! The sturdy and
straightforward temperament of the resilient king Pizuma is
splendidly reflected here.

Collector Renta: Thank you so much! I not only want you to
receive the reward, but also my gratitude.
実績 立ちはだかる大盾

Collector Renta: Take a look at this crown! I had it
displayed in the most magnificent place!
